### 1. Build & Project Configuration

The build configurations configure core Jetpack Compose, Room compiler processing via KSP, WorkManager, and Dagger Hilt:

- **Root settings & plugins**: [settings.gradle.kts](file:///c:/Users/Kshitij%20Sharma/Desktop/Omnis/Magnum%20Opus/Personal%20Manager/settings.gradle.kts) and [build.gradle.kts](file:///c:/Users/Kshitij%20Sharma/Desktop/Omnis/Magnum%20Opus/Personal%20Manager/build.gradle.kts) at the root level define build setup and version catalog inclusions.
- **Module gradle configuration**: [app/build.gradle.kts](file:///c:/Users/Kshitij%20Sharma/Desktop/Omnis/Magnum%20Opus/Personal%20Manager/app/build.gradle.kts) configures namespace `com.productivity.app`, target SDK 34, and dependencies for Room, Hilt, Compose BOM, Navigation, and WorkManager.
- **System Manifest**: [AndroidManifest.xml](file:///c:/Users/Kshitij%20Sharma/Desktop/Omnis/Magnum%20Opus/Personal%20Manager/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml) registers essential permissions (`SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM`, `USE_EXACT_ALARM`, `RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED`, `POST_NOTIFICATIONS`) and declares `ReminderBootReceiver`.

